WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:02.109
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.109 --> 00:00:03.813
How have y'all been doing?

00:00:04.147 --> 00:00:05.480
I've been doing good.

00:00:05.480 --> 00:00:07.960
I just had this on my heart.

00:00:08.256 --> 00:00:13.920
I see so many people in the comments below saying, 'Please pray for me.

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:23.140
' I get a lot of emails from people asking for prayer for healing and deliverance, needing new body parts, new organs, and all kinds of stuff.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.535
There's nothing too big for our God.

00:00:26.535 --> 00:00:42.605
I want to encourage you today that whatever it may be—you may be on death's doorstep, just seconds away from stepping over into Glory—I believe with all my heart that it's never too late for a divine miracle.

00:00:42.605 --> 00:00:46.889
It's never too late for God to heal you wherever you are.

00:00:46.889 --> 00:01:05.159
If you're in the hospital and you're watching this right now on your phone or your laptop, or wherever you are at the hospital, or you may be in hospice, or at home and they've released you and told you you're going to die in so many days—I'm telling you, nothing is impossible for our Lord.

00:01:05.679 --> 00:01:09.340
All things are possible to him that believes.

00:01:09.735 --> 00:01:14.1000
I believe that he became sick so that we don't have to have sickness anymore.

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:23.869
Galatians says that Christ redeemed us from the curse of the law, and the curse of the law is everything in Deuteronomy 28.

00:01:23.869 --> 00:01:36.112
If you read all about Deuteronomy 28 and everything about sickness and disease, Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory over sickness and disease.

00:01:36.112 --> 00:01:38.040
Find scriptures to stand on.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:47.743
That's what we do in this house for every single thing we ever have need of—physically, financially, spiritually, or emotionally.

00:01:47.743 --> 00:01:51.222
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory.

00:01:51.457 --> 00:01:55.496
I just want to encourage you today: find scriptures.

00:01:55.496 --> 00:01:56.171
Google it.

00:01:56.171 --> 00:02:03.573
If you don't have Google on your phone, find a Bible app, put in there 'healing scriptures,' and read those scriptures.

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:05.570
Meditate on that word.

00:02:05.570 --> 00:02:13.377
Get that word down inside of your heart, and the word will become real to you and change your life.

00:02:13.377 --> 00:02:16.376
Every single day, get in that word.

00:02:17.048 --> 00:02:21.800
If the doctors prescribed you medicine, take the medicine and take the word.

00:02:23.846 --> 00:02:28.314
Read that word; let it go in through your eyes and get inside your spirit.

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:34.206
The more you feed on that word, the more the word becomes real to you.

00:02:34.206 --> 00:02:44.540
Just like when you take a prescription, sometimes it takes time for it to get in your system and to help you, but consistency is the key.

00:02:44.540 --> 00:02:48.509
I'm telling you, get in the word and the word will change you.

00:02:48.509 --> 00:02:51.884
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:02:52.101 --> 00:02:56.305
I want to encourage you today to call those things that be not.

00:02:56.305 --> 00:03:02.498
You may be dying or having a bad report; call those things that be not as though they were.

00:03:02.498 --> 00:03:05.319
'I am healed by the stripes of Jesus.

00:03:05.319 --> 00:03:09.640
Jesus bore all my sicknesses and took all my diseases.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:14.053
I don't have to have any of that in my body because Jesus paid the price.

00:03:14.053 --> 00:03:16.608
' If he took it, I don't need to bear it.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.620
Satan, I'm not taking your 'poo-poo package.

00:03:22.620 --> 00:03:34.425
' He comes all the time with the 'poo-poo package' full of all his doubt, unbelief, worry, and stuff telling you you're going to die, you're not going to make it, and there's no hope for you.

00:03:36.235 --> 00:03:49.180
But I'm telling you, Jesus has a plan for your life and he has encouragement for you today: 'Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:03:49.180 --> 00:03:55.952
' Jesus wants you to be in health and prosperity—physically, spiritually, and financially.

00:03:55.952 --> 00:03:58.359
He doesn't want anything bad for you.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:01.899
God is a good God and the devil is a bad devil.

00:04:02.169 --> 00:04:04.720
I'm telling you, he has a plan for your life.

00:04:09.927 --> 00:04:18.380
There are testimonies out there about people who have been delivered from sickness and disease.

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:25.960
I'm standing with a lady for her diabetes to be gone, and for Joyce with her kidneys.

00:04:36.589 --> 00:04:36.846
We are believing for the manifestation of whatever they need.

00:04:39.947 --> 00:04:42.589
Sometimes there's a process.

00:04:42.589 --> 00:04:47.260
We see healing gradually sometimes, but sometimes it's instantaneous.

00:04:47.260 --> 00:05:02.365
No matter how you get your manifestation, it's like when Noah sent out the dove to go find land and he came back with an olive leaf—just a little bitty thing.

00:05:02.365 --> 00:05:13.767
It wasn't a huge sycamore tree leaf; it was just a little bitty thing, but it gave him encouragement to know the flood was over.

00:05:13.767 --> 00:05:16.171
There's a change coming.

00:05:18.996 --> 00:05:23.366
You may just get that little bitty glimmer of hope.

00:05:25.070 --> 00:05:27.952
Don't say, 'It's too small a thing.

00:05:27.952 --> 00:05:30.707
' No, that means something's changing.

00:05:30.707 --> 00:05:33.149
We already see the ship turning around.

00:05:33.149 --> 00:05:39.560
You've got to get excited whenever you see just a little bitty leaf.

00:05:41.823 --> 00:06:06.000
That little dove put it in its little beak—a little bitty bird went out there and grabbed a hold of something and brought it back for encouragement, showing that the flood's over.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:11.479
Today is your day of turnaround.

00:06:11.479 --> 00:06:13.429
Don't despise small beginnings.

00:06:13.429 --> 00:06:20.057
Get excited about the little things.

00:06:20.057 --> 00:06:25.840
That's what I do with my daughter Megan.

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:43.164
We went to church as a family and sat in one of the most amazing churches in Tulsa, Oklahoma, this last week.

00:06:46.180 --> 00:06:47.484
It blessed us a lot.

00:06:53.964 --> 00:07:11.790
We hadn't been to church in a long time because ushers have often asked us to leave because Megan was causing a commotion and was disruptive.

00:07:11.790 --> 00:07:18.819
But this time she didn't act out.

00:07:23.146 --> 00:07:32.067
I just want to tell you all, that was a miracle in itself.

00:07:32.067 --> 00:07:44.977
Nobody even knew it, because nobody knew us at this church, but it was a miracle.

00:07:44.977 --> 00:07:59.156
Regardless of how small it may have been in somebody's eyes, it was a big miracle to us.

00:07:59.156 --> 00:08:19.960
We saw that little leaf in that dove's mouth and we rejoiced all the way home and gave God the praise for it.

00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:36.479
Another testimony about her: for 14 years, she wouldn't go to the dentist.

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:49.385
They weren't able to touch her teeth because she'd bite them.

00:08:52.057 --> 00:09:02.571
Then one day, I told Megan, 'Hey baby, Daddy's taking you to the dentist tomorrow.

00:09:02.571 --> 00:09:10.040
Please don't bite the doctor; keep your mouth open.

00:09:10.040 --> 00:09:30.293
' I got some tools from Amazon and I tried to pretend like I was the dentist, practicing.

00:09:30.293 --> 00:09:46.560
We went to the dentist that day, and she got X-rays and a full cleaning.

00:09:46.560 --> 00:10:06.044
She let the doctor open her mouth and look in there, and after all those years, she didn't have one cavity.

00:10:06.044 --> 00:10:32.847
What I'm trying to tell you is that you can't give up when it seems impossible and looks like it's never going to change.

00:10:32.847 --> 00:10:46.320
You've got to believe God and know that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:55.489
This was one of those things that seemed impossible.

00:10:55.489 --> 00:11:04.976
But God, who is rich in Mercy, made it possible.

00:11:04.976 --> 00:11:10.746
We stood for that for 14 years.

00:11:10.746 --> 00:11:19.728
Then, for 17 years, we believed for her to be potty trained.

00:11:19.728 --> 00:11:38.013
One day she woke up, went and sat on the stool, and she's never had an accident since.

00:11:38.013 --> 00:11:43.519
She's been potty trained ever since.

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:47.126
God's been faithful.

00:11:47.126 --> 00:11:58.320
It took 17 going on 18 years of no change, and then suddenly it changed overnight.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:05.960
What seems impossible in your life, God can turn around.

00:12:11.084 --> 00:12:18.609
I want to show you these testimonies about people God touched.

00:12:27.012 --> 00:12:29.279
A boy had cancer; another woman had incurable heart disease.

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:35.120
Jesus will touch you, too.

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:49.119
He's no respecter of persons, and what he'll do for one, he will do for you.

00:12:49.119 --> 00:13:02.396
I'll be right back after these testimonies, and I'm going to come and pray for you today.

00:13:02.396 --> 00:13:17.440
I worked at Victory Church for about 13 years and started getting the reputation that if I prayed for you, Jesus would heal you.

00:13:18.620 --> 00:13:32.560
There was this lady whose little boy was diagnosed with cancer that was eating up the side of his face.

00:13:32.825 --> 00:14:03.124
I was the janitor there, and I was cleaning a room when she came to me and said, 'Hey Brandon, I heard that if you would pray for my little boy, God would heal him.

00:14:03.124 --> 00:14:12.924
' He was about seven or eight years old.

00:14:12.924 --> 00:14:24.813
She said he had a massive tumor on the side of his face.

00:14:24.813 --> 00:14:37.680
It was shocking because it was the size of a mandarin orange.

00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:52.440
I laid hands on that tumor, cursed it, and told it to go in the name of Jesus.

00:14:55.824 --> 00:15:07.288
I felt electricity go out of my fingers, and the power of God went into that tumor.

00:15:09.235 --> 00:15:22.178
I told her to rejoice for the rest of the night because I believed the Lord was healing that tumor.

00:15:28.871 --> 00:15:39.040
The next week, she came back and said she took her son to the doctor to get a certificate of health.

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:45.014
That tumor was completely gone.

00:15:46.955 --> 00:16:10.309
The doctor said he'd never seen anything like it and tried to say it had to be a plugged lymph node because cancer doesn't just disappear.

00:16:10.309 --> 00:16:27.859
But she told him about all the blood work and the chemo they were wanting to start.

00:16:27.859 --> 00:16:39.898
They tried to downplay it, but we both knew—I touched it, and it was really gnarly.

00:16:39.898 --> 00:16:45.314
But God touched that little boy.

00:16:45.314 --> 00:16:48.987
Now, another testimony.

00:16:58.440 --> 00:16:58.667
I was mowing my grandmother's yard.

00:16:58.667 --> 00:17:05.049
She's almost 90, and I try to help her out.

00:17:10.664 --> 00:17:20.774
I was just minding my own business, praying in the spirit while I mowed.

00:17:20.774 --> 00:17:38.819
There was this African-American man walking down the street with an oxygen tank.

00:17:42.916 --> 00:17:54.449
He was a weird shade of gray, and he was gasping for air.

00:17:58.502 --> 00:18:06.215
The Lord said, 'Get off that mower right now and go pray for that man.

00:18:06.215 --> 00:18:17.831
' I wrestled with it for a bit, but then I obeyed.

00:18:31.793 --> 00:18:37.067
I walked down and told him, 'This may sound wild, but the Lord told me to come pray for you.

00:18:37.067 --> 00:18:39.550
Is it okay?

00:18:39.550 --> 00:18:49.580
' He looked flustered and said, 'I guess so.

00:18:49.580 --> 00:18:52.780
I'm dying.

00:18:52.780 --> 00:19:14.160
' He had sprayed Roundup on ditches for the government for 35 years, and the toxic fumes destroyed his lungs.

00:19:14.160 --> 00:19:28.040
He needed a lung transplant and the doctor said he was dying.

00:19:44.392 --> 00:19:44.676
I took authority over his lungs and prayed.

00:19:46.774 --> 00:19:53.560
I didn't feel anything—it was like touching a cold stove.

00:19:53.560 --> 00:20:01.063
But I told him, 'I believe you're healed today.

00:20:01.063 --> 00:20:11.384
' A couple of weeks later, he ran up to me.

00:20:11.384 --> 00:20:16.440
He said he'd been completely healed, with two brand-new lungs.

00:20:16.440 --> 00:20:29.120
They took him off the donor list and he didn't need the oxygen tank anymore.

00:20:29.120 --> 00:20:34.813
His skin was back to its healthy color.

00:20:35.147 --> 00:20:49.164
He wasn't even a Christian yet, so I witnessed to him and led him to the Lord.

00:20:49.164 --> 00:20:52.140
Now, another story.

00:21:05.976 --> 00:21:06.304
I was leading prayer on a Saturday.

00:21:06.304 --> 00:21:20.139
Suddenly, I saw an angel dive-bomb from the ceiling like a rocket with a heart in his hand.

00:21:20.139 --> 00:21:21.235
He dropped that heart inside a lady's chest.

00:21:21.235 --> 00:21:29.760
I called her up and told her the Lord wanted to heal her.

00:21:29.760 --> 00:21:38.462
The power of God knocked her down, and she was crying and rejoicing.

00:21:49.868 --> 00:21:50.320
The next week, she ran into the church so excited.

00:21:52.490 --> 00:22:00.340
She had a doctor's appointment and told the doctor she believed she was healed.

00:22:01.030 --> 00:22:08.586
She had started exercising and jogging without getting winded.

00:22:16.309 --> 00:22:16.663
The doctor checked her heart and was shocked—it was like brand-new.

00:22:16.663 --> 00:22:21.885
He gave her a certificate of health.

00:22:23.919 --> 00:22:38.480
She told me her husband was a Jewish atheist who was angry because her heart condition prevented her from doing anything at home.

00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:54.160
But because of her healing, he gave his heart to Jesus and started coming to church.

00:23:01.931 --> 00:23:04.594
The doctor had said if they even tried surgery on her artery, she wouldn't make it.

00:23:04.594 --> 00:23:10.291
But God completely healed her.

00:23:10.291 --> 00:23:18.680
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:23:28.008 --> 00:23:28.224
Look at the story of the woman with the issue of blood.

00:23:33.869 --> 00:23:47.749
She spent all she had and grew worse, but she touched the hem of his garment and virtue went out of him.

00:23:47.749 --> 00:23:55.756
Virtue is going to come through this camera today.

00:23:55.756 --> 00:24:09.884
Just like with blind Bartimaeus, son of Timaeus, if he did it then, he'll do it now.

00:24:09.884 --> 00:24:15.016
You just have to have simple faith.

00:24:15.016 --> 00:24:20.195
Go watch my video about the crucifixion.

00:24:20.195 --> 00:24:36.230
Jesus took me out of my body and showed me what he did for us on that cross.

00:24:36.230 --> 00:24:41.070
Let's pray for your miracle today.

00:24:41.070 --> 00:24:44.995
I'm going to agree with you.

00:24:44.995 --> 00:24:59.768
Where two are touching and agreeing, let's do it by faith through the camera.

00:25:11.953 --> 00:25:12.159
You may have AIDS, cancer, or diabetes—nothing is too big.

00:25:12.159 --> 00:25:20.789
Father, I thank you right now for every single person believing for a manifestation of healing.

00:25:20.789 --> 00:25:28.779
We call them healed, whole, and well in Jesus' name.

00:25:28.779 --> 00:25:40.928
We call healing over stroke victims, arthritis, diabetes, and heart disease.

00:25:40.928 --> 00:25:55.100
We're calling those things that be not as though they were.

00:25:55.100 --> 00:26:01.034
We call the manifestation done now.

00:26:01.034 --> 00:26:15.347
Faith is the substance of things hoped for and the evidence of things not seen.

00:26:15.347 --> 00:26:23.874
We receive your healing power from all disease and demonic oppression.

00:26:23.874 --> 00:26:29.240
PTSD, I command you to leave right now in the name of Jesus.

00:26:29.240 --> 00:26:46.124
I call you delivered from the flashbacks and for your mind to be lined up with the word of God.

00:26:46.124 --> 00:27:04.906
Second Timothy 1:7 says God has not given you a spirit of fear but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:27:04.906 --> 00:27:17.973
Father, I thank you for the children with autism, Down syndrome, cerebral palsy, or learning disabilities.

00:27:17.973 --> 00:27:30.829
We call healing and wholeness over their bodies in the name of Jesus.

00:27:30.829 --> 00:27:43.906
We thank you that you bore it all on the cross.

00:27:43.906 --> 00:27:53.229
We thank you for deliverance from drugs and alcohol.

00:28:01.093 --> 00:28:05.200
I call cirrhosis of the liver healed and whole.

00:28:05.200 --> 00:28:12.760
Drug addictions, meth, opioids—we call them delivered.

00:28:14.919 --> 00:28:27.007
We thank you for marriages being restored and families coming back together.

00:28:37.749 --> 00:28:38.039
We call the generational curses and strongholds broken in Jesus' name.

00:28:38.039 --> 00:28:46.589
You are set free from alcoholism and addiction.

00:28:59.648 --> 00:28:59.964
You walk in victory.

00:28:59.964 --> 00:29:06.708
Jesus loves you and doesn't want you to suffer.

00:29:06.708 --> 00:29:20.750
He wants you to have a good life and an expected end.

00:29:45.380 --> 00:29:45.933
I hope this encouraged you.

00:29:45.933 --> 00:30:09.650
If it did, please subscribe, click the notification bell, and give a thumbs up.

00:30:09.650 --> 00:30:20.600
Comment down below if you were healed or set free today.

00:30:20.600 --> 00:30:26.405
People need to hear encouragement.

00:30:39.235 --> 00:30:39.577
God bless you all in Jesus' name.

00:30:39.577 --> 00:30:50.445
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:30:50.445 --> 00:30:56.100
We'll see you next time.

00:30:56.100 --> 00:30:57.180
Bye-bye.
